==German==
===Etymology===
While geographically not really correct (some parts of ''West'' Germany lie to the East of East Germany), historically used to distinguish the ''Bundesrepublik Deutschland'' from the ''Deutsche Demokratische Republik''.
===Noun===
'''Ostdeutschland''' ''n''
# Eastern Germany, the former German Democratic Republic
